name: Black Squadron TIE
Lore: 'Part of Vader''s hand-picked squadron stationed at the Death Star. Boasts the latest in Imperial weaponry. Each pilot and starfighter is at the peak of readiness.',
Text: 'Deploy -2 to Death Star or same location as Vader. Permanent pilot aboard provides ability of 2 and adds 2 to power. Adds 1 to its weapon destiny draws.',
